---
title: Spiced Chopped Lamb Steak with Tomato Relish and Roasted Potatoes
description: A thing of such delicious, dribble-down-your-chin simplicity, the noble chopped lamb steak can be re-invented time and time again to create the most divine dinnertime results. For this little incarnation, we’ve taken ground lamb and thrown in a twist with a oh so tasty tomato chutney!
